{"text_id":168940,"tokens":["Evolution"," of"," the"," adaptive"," immune"," system"," occurred"," in"," an"," ancestor"," of"," the"," jaw","ed"," vertebrates","."," Many"," of"," the"," classical"," molecules"," of"," the"," adaptive"," immune"," system"," (","e",".","g",".,"," immun","oglo","bul","ins"," and"," T"," cell"," receptors",")"," are"," not"," present"," in"," the"," jaw","less"," vertebrates"," (","lamp","rey"," and"," hag","fish","),"," while"," molecules"," with"," similar"," functions"," are"," found"," in"," the"," jaw","ed"," vertebrates"," (","tele","ost"," fish"," and"," tetra","pods",")"," and"," the"," invertebrate"," deuter","ost","omes"," (","ech","in","oder","ms"," and"," uro","chord","ates",")."," The"," adaptive"," immune"," system"," of"," jaw","less"," vertebrates"," is"," thought"," to"," more"," closely"," resemble"," the"," innate"," immune"," system",","," utilizing"," a"," diverse"," repertoire"," of"," variable"," lymphocyte"," receptors"," (","V","LR","s",")"," to"," recognize"," polymorphic"," targets","."," In"," this"," review",","," I"," summarize"," what"," is"," known"," about"," the"," molecules"," involved"," in"," adaptive"," immunity"," in"," the"," jaw","less"," vertebrates"," and"," discuss"," how"," the"," presence"," of"," molecules"," similar"," to"," those"," of"," the"," adaptive"," immune"," system"," in"," the"," invertebrate"," deuter","ost","omes"," can"," inform"," our"," understanding"," of"," the"," origins"," of"," adaptive"," immunity","."," In"," addition",","," I"," present"," a"," hypothesis"," for"," the"," molecular"," basis"," of"," MHC"," class"," I"," recognition"," by"," the"," adaptive"," immune"," system"," in"," the"," jaw","less"," vertebrates","."," The"," immune"," system"," has"," evolved"," in"," animals"," to"," protect"," them"," from"," infectious"," agents"," and"," other"," pathogens","."," Immune"," systems"," are"," generally"," divided"," into"," two"," components",":"," innate"," immunity",","," which"," is"," found"," in"," all"," meta","zo","ans"," and"," is"," the"," first"," line"," of"," defense"," against"," pathogens",","," and"," adaptive"," immunity",","," which"," is"," specific"," to"," jaw","ed"," vertebrates"," and"," certain"," invertebrates","."," Adaptive"," immunity"," is"," able"," to"," \"","adapt","\""," to"," the"," specific"," anti","genic"," makeup"," of"," an"," invading"," pathogen",","," allowing"," the"," host"," to"," retain"," a"," \"","memory","\""," of"," previously"," encountered"," pathogens","."," This"," enables"," the"," host"," to"," mount"," a"," more"," effective"," response"," against"," re","infection"," by"," the"," same"," pathogen","."," The"," immune"," system"," of"," vertebrates"," consists"," of"," two"," main"," branches",":"," the"," innate"," immune"," system"," and"," the"," adaptive"," immune"," system","."," The"," innate"," immune"," system",","," which"," is"," the"," first"," line"," of"," defense"," against"," pathogens",","," is"," present"," in"," all"," meta","zo","ans",","," including"," vertebrates"," and"," invertebrates",","," while"," the"," adaptive"," immune"," system",","," which"," is"," specific"," to"," jaw","ed"," vertebrates"," and"," some"," invertebrates",","," develops"," only"," after"," exposure"," to"," a"," specific"," pathogen","."," The"," molecular"," basis"," of"," adaptive"," immunity"," in"," vertebrates"," is"," thought"," to"," be"," due"," to"," the"," emergence"," of"," recombination","-","activating"," gene"," (","RAG",")"," gene"," products"," (","RAG","1"," and"," RAG","2",")"," and"," TCR"," and"," B","CR"," gene"," rearrangement"," (","1",","," ","2",")."," The"," adaptive"," immune"," system",","," in"," contrast"," to"," the"," innate"," immune"," system",","," is"," able"," to"," generate"," a"," diverse"," array"," of"," receptors"," capable"," of"," recognizing"," a"," diverse"," array"," of"," antigens","."," The"," molecular"," mechanisms"," of"," adaptive"," immunity"," in"," jaw","less"," vertebrates"," are"," not"," known","."," Studies"," of"," the"," adaptive"," immune"," system"," in"," jaw","less"," vertebrates"," have"," identified"," a"," diverse"," repertoire"," of"," variable"," lymphocyte"," receptors"," (","V","LR","s",")"," capable"," of"," recognizing"," polymorphic"," targets"," (","3","-","1","0",")."," Recent"," studies"," of"," the"," adaptive"," immune"," system"," in"," invertebrate"," deuter","ost","omes"," (","ech","in","oder","ms"," and"," uro","chord","ates",")"," have"," identified"," TCR","-","like"," and"," Ig","-","like"," molecules"," capable"," of"," recognizing"," a"," diverse"," array"," of"," antigens"," (","1","1",","," ","1","2",")."," Thus",","," it"," is"," possible"," that"," the"," jaw","less"," vertebrates",","," like"," the"," invertebrate"," deuter","ost","omes",","," have"," an"," adaptive"," immune"," system"," based"," on"," a"," repertoire"," of"," diverse"," receptors"," with"," limited"," somatic"," diversity","."," In"," the"," present"," review",","," I"," will"," summarize"," the"," current"," knowledge"," of"," the"," adaptive"," immune"," system"," in"," jaw","less"," vertebrates"," and"," discuss"," how"," the"," presence"," of"," molecules"," similar"," to"," those"," of"," the"," adaptive"," immune"," system"," in"," the"," invertebrate"," deuter","ost","omes"," can"," inform"," our"," understanding"," of"," the"," origins"," of"," adaptive"," immunity","."," In"," addition",","," I"," will"," discuss"," the"," molecular"," basis"," of"," MHC"," class"," I"," recognition"," by"," the"," adaptive"," immune"," system"," in"," jaw","less"," vertebrates","."," As"," with"," the"," jaw","ed"," vertebrates",","," the"," adaptive"," immune"," system"," of"," jaw","less"," vertebrates"," can"," be"," divided"," into"," two"," main"," components",":"," the"," lymphoid"," and"," myeloid"," lineages","."," The"," lymphoid"," lineage"," is"," made"," up"," of"," lymphocytes"," that"," are"," capable"," of"," undergoing"," cl","onal"," expansion"," and"," differentiation","."," These"," lymphocytes"," are"," responsible"," for"," antigen"," recognition"," and"," cl","onal"," expansion","."," The"," myeloid"," lineage"," is"," made"],"sub_source":"squad","model":"65B","label":1}